<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-05-0563 </DOCNO><TEXT>Juridical aspects of renewable energy prospecting, mining or production,and utilization are reviewed and analysed (in the French context). Theurbanistic and building construction constraints concerning the solarenergy reception in a residential building are discussed. The variousincitements (subventions, subsidies, fiscality...) for the developmentof renewable energies in France are also reviewed with the example ofthe french energy conservation agency (AFME).</TEXT></DOC>